pageContext.claim: “Look what happened for Ted Cruz; who's doing great now -- we left Houston, he's now doing great -- they don't even talk about that race and his opponent is not very good.”
pageContext.analysis: The polls show the race between Sen. Ted Cruz (R-Texas) and Rep. Beto O'Rourke (D) have tightened since Trump's rally for Cruz. Beto raised far more money than Cruz.
